linux is a kernel, os, and huge open-source success.
the linux penguin so is funny-looking because it is fat.
the penguin's name is Tux.
a distro is short for Linux distribution.
a distro is an operating system which uses the Linux kernel, but does its own thing at the application level.
GNU is an acronym for GNU's not Unix.
GNU is a way for people to use a product like Unix for free and for programmers anywhere and everywhere to contribute to this and other related open-source projects.
I should care what the Free Software Foundation thinks because they do in fact have good ideas about high-quality coding and a better working environment through free and open source software.
